ysit so they can eat and sleep.  Did you sit at ragefire the whole time or did someone else help you?  I see nothing exciting about having to kill placeholders that are so trivial to me it's not even funny.  I see nothing enticing about having to play 6+ hours a night every night a week to get anywhere.  <br>
